Class ResourceNavigator

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class ResourceNavigator
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    The ResourceNavigator is a multiple tabbed bar that contains all the available resources. These resources will be displayed as tables with their stats. These tables can be clicked and dragged to the map to place the respective resource.
    Author:
    Nick Schmidt
